pageContext.claim: “We're the number-one tester for this virus in the entire world. There's nobody close. We did almost 14 million tests. Number two is Germany at 3 million. South Kor- -- I think South Korea -- probably at about almost 3 million.”
pageContext.analysis: Actually, Russia at the time was second with about 8 million tests. South Korea conducted about 800,000 tests.
